structure.unit: Chapter 17B METROPOLITAN MIAMI-DADE COUNTY DEMOLITION OF UNINHABITABLE STRUCTURES ORDINANCE

text.section:
Sec. 17B-4. Existing remedies preserved.
The provisions of this chapter shall be cumulative and supplemental to and not in derogation of any provisions of the Florida Statutes, the Code of Metropolitan Miami-Dade County or any other applicable law.
